Salma Hayek, 55, proved her bikini body has not faltered since her infamous From Dusk Till Dawn scene as she donned a plunging black bikini. The stunning actress posed against the tranquil backdrop of sea and palm trees as she covered her shoulders with a black and white kimono. Salma accessorised with a black hat and dark sunglasses to shield her eyes. The day before, the brunette received a wave of praise when she shared a “no makeup” selfie to showcase her natural beauty. Ella gushed: “You look good,” while Art exclaimed: “Forever incredible.”